name: 猛男跑酷（Strong man parkour）
description: Get ready to challenge gravity, jump like never before, and experience the exhilarating world of parkour from a new perspective. This is a casual game. This is the ultimate parkour challenge that will push your skills to the limit, traverse complex obstacles, climb towering mountains, and win. There was no turning back from the beginning; One mistake, you will fall all the way. Are you ready to prove your parkour ability and reach the top?
